overview: The user initiated a review of their sleep questionnaire application,
  providing a detailed specification and Statement of Work. The agent performed
  a comprehensive code review, identifying several critical gaps in the
  implementation, such as the absence of a tiredness severity scale, COMISA
  detection, insufficient sleep syndrome detection, and weighted EDS scoring.
  The agent then proceeded to implement these missing features, enhancing the
  questionnaire's diagnostic capabilities and report generation. Additionally,
  the CSV export functionality was expanded to include all questionnaire data,
  and new questions for pain severity and chronic fatigue screening were
  integrated. The outcome is a more robust and feature-complete sleep
  questionnaire application that aligns more closely with the original
  requirements.
